data.text:
Rollo was an enormous biker from Frisco, with a dark crewcut sporting a bleached blond lightning bolt.

He had a relationship with Marlene. Later when Marlene was with Case, he suspected that Rollo was still occasional boyfriend.

Rollo had a Frisco flamethrower, like a fat anglehead flashlight, which he called his "dragon". For some reason it was stored in the hotel that Case and Marlene spent a summer month.
